The peripheral-region tables under `mmio/` are derived from:

    RH850/F1KH, RH850/F1KM Hardware User's Manual
    Document R01UH0684EJ0130, Revision 1.30 (Renesas Electronics, 2021-09-30)
    Sections 4A.3 / 4B.3 / 4C.3 — Peripheral I/O Address Map

Renesas Electronics Corporation retains copyright on the original
manual. The CSV data here is a factual re-statement of those tables,
reproduced for interoperability with third-party disassembly and
reverse-engineering tools (analogous to a vendor SVD file). The
extraction script under `tools/` is provided so anyone can re-derive
the data from their own copy of the manual.
